{"tid":642295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖！廣州男為瑣事殺妻　割頭後拎住隨街走","createTime":"2018-04-25T16:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T23:10:08.000Z","uid":179810,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"be8f034e45501137ebb1bb63a96fff85840b1044","tid":642295,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/mobile/bkncn-20180425190022236-0425_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180425%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180425190022236-0425_05011_001.html&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb375jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=fd9be255\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/mobile/bkncn-20180425190022236-0425_05011_001.html</a><br />\n入面有片<br />\n<br />\n廣州海珠區周三（25日）發生一宗駭人兇殺案，一名31歲張姓男子因家庭糾紛，在位於康樂村的家中殺死妻子後，先用刀將她的頭顱割下，再提着頭顱走到街頭，過程被街上的閉路電視拍下。事後警方通報，指張男已於當日上午投案自首，案件目前仍在調查中。 <br />\n<br />\n警方通報指，張男是湖北人，他供稱因為家庭糾紛而將28歲夏姓妻子殺害。從網傳閉路電視片段顯示，張男行兇後拿着疑似頭顱的物體走出一幢大樓，並大搖大擺地在街上行走；當時有不少居民在張男身邊經過，但似乎未有查覺，均如常行走。網上有消息指，當時張男提着頭顱，由家中一直走到鷺江地鐵站。 <br />\n<br />\n案發後，有清潔工人在康樂村附近的垃圾桶內發現一個疑似女性的人頭，嚇得大聲呼喊；附近居民聞聲而至，立即報警求助。居民指，上午11時，警方將死者遺體蓋上白布從案發單位抬出，及後看到警員帶疑兇到場指認。至下午2時許，涉事單位已被貼上封條，禁止非調查人員進入。據報，事發大樓內的樓梯亦血漬斑斑。 <br />\n<br />\n有居於案發單位旁的居民向內地傳媒表示，事發前未聽到任何奇怪聲音，直到有警察趕到現場，他們才知道發生了命案。另一名王姓居民則表示，當日上午8時許與友人路經鳳發菜市場時，看到一名疑為兇手的男子走過；當時看到他提着疑似人頭的不明物迎面走過，「他身上、鞋上都是血，我們都嚇壞了」。"},{"pid":"a609a325e5d0f2373bcb06a9d2c9f5cb6ddff2a5","tid":642295,"uid":65526,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"厲害了"},{"pid":"2e2fc7e1e44f77e85b64d9d771092dfb48a31740","tid":642295,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"講真大陸你拎住炸彈自自然然咁行都無人理你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ed904a2687b3e6a8d72735bd91dbe346ce134f","tid":642295,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"d人好似當無野發生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb9830406421b880e29aacb8d21fe4e289f9221","tid":642295,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ed904a2687b3e6a8d72735bd91dbe346ce134f","tid":642295,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"d人好似當無野發生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"支那日常<br />\n<br />\n你岩岩出世?"},{"pid":"2f64f9577b40aec96e88657e672be401bf44215c","tid":642295,"uid":6774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要行咗咁遠都冇人理 係最後抌走咗先比個清潔工人發現 厲害了"},{"pid":"7417c50333ad57ccbc69a1b897287b1fc0ee9669","tid":642295,"uid":99205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"87ed904a2687b3e6a8d72735bd91dbe346ce134f","tid":642295,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"d人好似當無野發生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T20:33:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170218/bkncn-20170218170235361-0218_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170218%2Fbkncn-20170218170235361-0218_05011_001.html&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb375jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=36673b82\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170218/bkncn-20170218170235361-0218_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<strong>武漢麵館老闆疑語帶譏諷　遭惡客斬死割頭</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170218/photo/bkncn-20170218170235361-0218_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170219203757\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170218%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170218170235361-0218_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170219203757&h=679591d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖北武漢今日中午發生駭人兇殺案。武昌火車站附近一間麵店的食客，在結帳時質疑店方收費過高，網傳疑兇覺得收費較此前貴了1元而埋怨，復遭老闆語帶譏諷說了一句：「吃不起就別吃。」該食客一怒之下，隨手在麵館拿起一把菜刀，將麵店老闆狂斬致死，其後更將其頭部割下，棄於垃圾桶內。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方通報稱，事發於中午12時25分，涉案的22歲胡姓男子（四川宣漢人）已當場被抓獲。通報又指，胡男與42歲的姚姓店主（湖北鄖西人）發生口角，胡男其後取去麵館一把菜刀，將姚男斬死。警方已將案件定性為故意殺人。目前，案件詳情仍在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的照片可見，死者頭部染血，而且前額頭骨更被砍開，畫面非常恐怖。"},{"pid":"ea89cd158c60dfcaf33f3f7b642488dcc20f9790","tid":642295,"uid":113183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:36:17.000Z","msg":"湖北人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2223464ad79aababd0228c21481a5bbe320834","tid":642295,"uid":5900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:45:24.000Z","msg":"湖北湖南，男嘅賊，女嘅雞<br />\n<br />\n垃圾縣"},{"pid":"92be15134cc015cd90ae46947676f0c7ba611eb7","tid":642295,"uid":99205,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:49:40.000Z","msg":"斬人頭啫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對羸國來講好小事<br />\n優勝劣敗<br />\n最緊要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>羸<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b7d2389ce868e49d6bbc5d98b9013f2099405123","tid":642295,"uid":99205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斬人頭啫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對<del>羸</del>贏國來講好小事<br />\n優勝劣敗<br />\n最緊要<del>羸</del>贏<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong></strong></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a91833923b6858172e01218bb362ead38ca5d063","tid":642295,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d91d5abc06b14f39c633d2fd2cb21df1fb7b3ac","tid":642295,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score